com.vernalis.core - package com.vernalis.core
This package contains a simple client to connect to RESTful web services (GET and POST operations).
com.vernalis.pdbconnector - package com.vernalis.pdbconnector
This package implements the main KNIME node classes for PdbConnector.
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config - package com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config
This package implements (non-KNIME related) classes used to define the query and report options supported by the PDB advanced search and custom report web services.
